Fresh Pi session: VERIFY REFACTORING PRESERVED BEHAVIOR.

Inputs:
- Latest refactor summary under {{run.dir}}/tdd/
- Repository constraints: {{run.dir}}/design/repository-constraints.md
- Worktree: {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Independently prove the refactoring changed design without changing behavior.

Rules:
- Do not edit or commit files.
- Run the focused and relevant prior tests.
- Inspect the refactoring diff for scope creep, speculative abstraction, test weakening, or behavioral changes.
- Produce concrete actionable findings only.

Write:
- Report: {{run.dir}}/tdd/refactor-verification-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/tdd/refactor-verification-status-{{run.round}}.json
- On failure: {{run.dir}}/tdd/refactor-verification-issues-{{run.round}}.json

Status examples:
{"status":"pass","summary":"refactoring preserved behavior","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"refactoring verification failed","issues_file":"tdd/refactor-verification-issues-{{run.round}}.json"}
